1. Find, create and move public_html folder, database folder, and email folder to USB drive
2. Install Dovecot and Postfix
3. Install Webanalyzer
4. Install cPanel or some type of Web Panel interface
5. Install firewall, add open ports 22, 443, 80, 8080, 9000
6. Install Webmail system
7. Install phpMyAdmin
8. Install RKHunter and other security utilities
9. Install Spam Assassin
10. Create web scripts (startweb.sh, stopweb.sh, reloadweb.sh, emailpurge.sh, etc)
11. Create cron jobs for auto update cert from let's encrypt'
12. Create menu system in case of failure of install
13. Create system for managing web server
14. Create deploy system from fresh install of Raspberian to setup ssh keys, boot options, localisation options, etc
15. Have ability for multiple choice applications and file server
16. Research message server applications
17. Research proxy server applications

